title: Nesting Stars Toy
description: What's Included: Set of 5x nesting stars. Shooting stars are lighting up the Danish town of Aarhus to make their way to your child's playroom. Little ones will love matching the muted colors while exploring their fine motor skills with this beautiful nesting star toy set. With our Danish Hygge collection of toys for kids 10 months - 3 years, your child can play while learning valuable skills and a little about Denmark—a charming country home to beautiful buildings and our favorite fairy tales. Details Made from 100% non toxic, BPA, BPS, PVC and phthalate free plastic. Recommended for ages 10 months to 3 yearsmk, Develops hand-eye coordination and helps with balance, gripping strength control, gross motor skills, and crossing midline exercises. Made in Denmark. Care To clean, wash with warm, soapy water and let air dry.
